{"tid":1827252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嫌未夠柒 陳偉霆將會出席2020央視春晚將《野狼Disco》改編成《過年Disco》","createTime":"2020-01-16T22:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:40:18.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8928b2bfb0d32cb7031f23bc391ff3952ffb53","tid":1827252,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T22:39:55.000Z","msg":"2020央視春晚首次於北京進行聯合綵排，今次央視春晚受熱捧程度被稱之為「流量盛宴」，一開場有TFBOYS、李現、鄭爽、楊紫、謝娜、吳磊、張藝興外，香港熟識的更有英皇的陳偉霆和惠英紅等，眾星齊集現身給觀眾拜年，而佟麗婭更是與央視名嘴們一起當主持人，在表演歌舞環節中，陳偉霆、張藝興、寶石將《野狼Disco》改編成《過年Disco》，陳偉霆的副歌和張藝興的rap相得益彰。易烊千璽、王嘉爾、羅志祥三位舞蹈達人共同帶來勁歌熱舞，帥氣十足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200115/photo/bkn-20200115200050509-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200115203921\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200115200050509-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200115203921&h=f3c20bda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0fc13edb599079bfd3be16f5346f971cce460e0","tid":1827252,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T22:41:35.000Z","msg":"柒到盡頭便是型<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa2dbdb5376a7af2535cb643f03f1ed7545bf7e","tid":1827252,"uid":247817,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"當年關家姐段片我睇到2020年都未睇曬，佢呢兩段都唔知要睇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e5de5385284836f71a6dde153bca72e1adde7d","tid":1827252,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:09:16.000Z","msg":"唔想知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f38ac94034bab776e0b8a3bbbcfad45afd0ec8c","tid":1827252,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T23:52:51.000Z","msg":"深女的化"},{"pid":"c288d737ee88c1c44810d80316facd22d8029ae9","tid":1827252,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":